Package: Retina
Type: Package
Title: Computer Vision Library for R
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-05-14
Authors@R: person("Simon", "Garnier", email = "garnier@njit.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3886-3974"))
Description: An OpenCV-based computer vision library providing an idiomatic R
    interface to image and video processing. Images are managed as R6 objects
    backed by OpenCV's cv::Mat (CPU) or cv::UMat (GPU).
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
